it.cnr.isti.labsedc.glimpse.example

Class MyGlimpseConsumer

  • java.lang.Object
    • it.cnr.isti.labsedc.glimpse.consumer.GlimpseAbstractConsumer
      • it.cnr.isti.labsedc.glimpse.example.MyGlimpseConsumer
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    GlimpseConsumer, javax.jms.MessageListener

    public class MyGlimpseConsumer
extends GlimpseAbstractConsumer
    This class is an example of how to extend the GlimpseAbstractConsumer class,
    simply implementing the abstract method messageReceived(Message).

    The behaviour of the class is defined in the GlimpseAbstractConsumer class and
    can be modified extending it or implementing the interface GlimpseConsumer.

    Version:
    3.2
    Author:
    Antonello Calabrò
